<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=euc-kr" />
    <title>01_pop전화상담신청</title>
    <!--<link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/favicon.ico"/>-->
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/lib/jquery-fakeform-0.5.js"></script>
    <script language="JavaScript" src="../../js/common.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/jquery-ui.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/base.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/layout.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/content.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/popup.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"  href="../../css/layout_direct.css" />
</head>
<body class="boxType">

<!--01_pop전화상담신청 : s-->
<!--layerPopWrap : s-->
<div class="dim_bg"></div>
<script>
    $(function(){
        $(document).on("change","input[name='insurance']",function(){
            var val = $(this).val();
            $(".insurance").hide();
            $(".insurance."+val).show();
        })
    })
</script>
<div class="layerPopWrap failjoin w600 tellApply">
    <div class="titleArea">
        <h2>전화상담 신청</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="popupContentArea">
        <div class="failimg phone">
            <h3 class="poinTit">고객님, 무엇을 도와드릴까요?</h3>
            <div class="con">
				상담신청을 남겨주시면, 전문 상담원이 직접 연락 드리겠습니다.
			</div>
        </div>
		<!--inputTable : s-->
		<div class="inputTable onlyInput bline">
            <!--2017-11-06 수정 : s-->
			<ul class="inputArea inlineBlock">
				<li class="item">
					<div class="selectItem">
						<select name="selectHp" id="telType" class="telType" title="연락처를 선택해주세요" style="width: 200px;">
							<option value="hpTypeCon">휴대폰</option>
							<option value="telTypeCon">자택</option>
							<option value="jobTypeCon">직장</option>
						</select>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li class="item">
                    <div class="selectTelType hpTypeCon">
                        <div class="inputBase" style="width: 330px;">
                            <label for="hpNumber">휴대폰번호 (‘-’없이)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="hpNumber" value="01087584589">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="selectTelType telTypeCon" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="selectItem">
                            <select name="selectTel" title="지역번호를 선택해주세요" style="width: 100px;">
                                <option value="02">02</option>
                                <option value="031">031</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="inputBase ml10" style="width: 220px;">
                            <label for="telNumber">전화번호 (‘-’없이)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="telNumber" value="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="selectTelType jobTypeCon" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="selectItem">
                            <select name="selectJob" title="지역번호를 선택해주세요" style="width: 100px;">
                                <option value="02">02</option>
                                <option value="031">031</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="inputBase ml10" style="width: 220px;">
                            <label for="jobNumber">전화번호 (‘-’없이)</label>
                            <input type="text" id="jobNumber" value="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
				</li>
			</ul>
            <!--2017-11-06 수정 : s-->

			<ul class="listStyle star">
				<li>상담전화 신청을 위한 연락처 수집·이용에 동의합니다.</li>
				<li>수집 정보는 상담 목적 외 용도로 이용되지 않습니다.</li>
			</ul>

		</div>
		<!--inputTable : e-->

		<!--btn:s-->
		<div class="btnAreaWrap tac">
            <a href="#" class="btn line inlineBlock gray" style="width: 150px;"><span>취소</span></a>
            <a href="#" class="btn line inlineBlock orange" style="width: 150px;"><span>전화상담 신청</span></a>
        </div>
		<!--btn:e-->


    </div>
    <a href="#" class="btnClose"><img src="https://direct.hi.co.kr/images/common/btn_popup_close.png" alt="닫기"></a>
</div>
<!--layerPopWrap : e-->
<!--01_pop전화상담신청 : e-->

</body>
</html>